   </prolog>
   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Click the All Tabs icon (<image placement="inline" href="../attachments/143899578/143899650.png"/>) and select <uicontrol>Config Settings</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select <uicontrol>Display Column Settings</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>From the <uicontrol>Display Type</uicontrol> list, select <uicontrol>Cart Line Item</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Add a new line and select <uicontrol>Guidance</uicontrol> for the <uicontrol>Field Name</uicontrol> or change an existing line.
               </p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image height="250"
                         placement="break"
                         width="289"
                         href="../attachments/143899578/143899649.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p> Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>. </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
      <result id="result_i3t_g33_rcc">The Guidance column is available in the Shopping
         Cart.</result>
   </body>
